{"tid":2239429,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"歡迎啲想砌模型嘅巴絲入黎 (49) 心急就訂模型，唔急就衝現啦","createTime":"2020-10-12T02:16:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T02:19:20.000Z","uid":9886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"77f24cce0f5a4440a84ca7ed83f3fb29a90f215d","tid":2239429,"uid":9886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T02:16:10.000Z","msg":"上一個post：<br />\n歡迎啲想砌模型嘅巴絲入黎 (48) 爆post唔開post爆膠爛件跌件痴塵斷刃<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2228642\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2228642</a><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">無論新手老手，呢個google site都包含左好多有用既資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/lihkg-model\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fview%2Flihkg-model&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBcQVtcXcndjic5JqfcA1BWo%3D&h=58d61720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/view/lihkg-model</a><br />\n<br />\n呢度不論係新手老手, 都一樣咁歡迎<br />\n絕對唔係小圈子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜模型種類都無任歡迎<br />\n有模型問題一定會有神通廣大既巴打幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問問題果陣，最好貼埋相，咁樣巴打們會易d 了解你個問題<br />\n<br />\n巴打們貼作品時，<br />\n請注明牌子、比例及模型名稱<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果轉貼，貼埋條link就正哂喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1001 請開新post"},{"pid":"9a2d7bdd673af94b40dc731aa7891944677729de","tid":2239429,"uid":343327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T02:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a60f7a8dde84ef4dea3245574af27d142b7d0ec2","tid":2239429,"uid":9886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T02:17:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5kjppHr.gif&amp;h=bb121e44&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"74c4fc95914c436256c5191d4b7d0ac6992eef47","tid":2239429,"uid":55949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T02:17:21.000Z","msg":"老子你做壞規矩"},{"pid":"3f57449bb1f5757b2a9a1a07cc31b297588b8a5e","tid":2239429,"uid":9886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T02:18:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家係點貼水貼 小弟成日較好哂位之後用棉花棒壓落去吸乾啲水就會移哂位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以下係我炒過無限咁多張水貼得出既經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 當你發現張貼開始可以離紙，你可以拎起佢用隻手指抹走水貼底紙d水，盡量唔好留太多水係張貼到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 水貼上左件，如果你見到有多餘既水珠可以用棉花棒吸走左佢先，之後先慢慢對位，如果開始發現郁唔到就可以點小小水再郁過直至岩位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 當你個位對好左，你就可以用棉花棒係其中一邊由水貼外碌入張貼，一到碌就可以壓實張水貼同埋吸水，吸水之餘又可以將d水推去另一邊 (手勢好你會見到d水係另一邊咇出黎) <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. Make sure 岩位，如果無問題壓好左我就會拎風筒吹一吹佢，唔洗完全乾晒係咁意就可以，之後係d 邊位落軟化劑 (點 / 印落去就可以，千千千千奇唔好抹落去，因為太多會起泡) 等一陣你就會見到d透明邊位開始收縮，完事就會靚仔晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8a8afadd54bd584ce93164bde774aa70b030966","tid":2239429,"uid":9886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74c4fc95914c436256c5191d4b7d0ac6992eef47","tid":2239429,"uid":55949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T02:17:21.000Z","msg":"老子你做壞規矩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T02:19:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2239431/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2239431/page/1</a><br />\n去呢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216858a8a25cefca3699b7472324e516cf21c462","tid":2239429,"uid":110265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T02:19:20.000Z","msg":"想典牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"a60f7a8dde84ef4dea3245574af27d142b7d0ec2","tid":2239429,"uid":9886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T02:17:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5kjppHr.gif&amp;h=bb121e44&amp;s=540\" />"}}